    <!-- Welcome Screen -->
    <string name="welcome_title">Welcome to My Savings!</string>
    <string name="welcome_para1">My Savings is a simple app designed to help you track your savings and spending. It\'s often hard to understand where your money goes or to see real progress in your savings, especially when it comes to money saved by giving up unnecessary purchases.</string>
    <string name="welcome_para2">Its main idea is to show you how you can save money and to visualize the effect of your savings. You will be able to mark your financial goals and track how your savings help you achieve them.</string>
    <string name="welcome_para3">This is your personal tool for a more conscious approach to finances.</string>
